NAME

    BioX::Workflow::Plugin::FileExists - a plugin to BioX::Workflow

SYNOPSIS

      biox-workflow.pl --plugins FileExists

DESCRIPTION

    BioX::Workflow::Plugin::FileExists is a plugin of BioX::Workflow that
    first checks that your local INPUT exists. If it doesn't exist it will
    exit with 256. If INPUT is empty it will give a warning. If OUTPUT is
    empty or doesn't exist it will give a warning.

